                <mxCell id="identity-note" value="Summary&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;GitHub team membership is translated into AWS IAM Identity Center permission sets.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Cluster accounts are assigned to permission sets.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Permission set roles are mapped to EKS Access Entries.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Cluster permissions are mapped to namespaces with RBAC groups.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=#82B366;fillColor=#D5E8D4;fontColor=#000000;fontStyle=0;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
