                <mxCell id="PaqEAZvtXvCs71vHTMZF-42" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 36px;&quot;&gt;Option 1 - New accounts in MP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1. New accounts created in MP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2. New infrastructure build in MP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3. Lattice service network shared to CP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4. DNS Points to ALB in MP account&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;5. Traffic routed back to CP from MP ALB&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;6. Traffic slowly migrated from CP to MP via weighted target groups&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;7. AWS resources rebuilt in MP and then migrated&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Issues and unknowns&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1. Cross account DNS from CP route 53 to MP ALB&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2. ALB with Nginx - is it possible? Will performance be ok?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3. Lattice - unknown tech, will the target groups work as expected?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4. Will still need to migrate all other AWS resources eg RDS etc to new account - big undertaking&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry height="705" width="540" x="1800" y="-1050" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
