                <mxCell id="PaqEAZvtXvCs71vHTMZF-208" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 36px;&quot;&gt;Final Architecture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1. Blue green achieved through ALB weighted target groups&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2. Separate VPC for Clusters and resources&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3. VPC Lattice used to simplify networking and make it easier to grow if needed&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Issues and unknowns&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1. ALB target groups vs DNS weighted records? Target groups gives us more control, DNS we are dependant on TTL and caching.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2. ALB with Nginx - is it possible? Will performance be ok? Is Nginx still needed with ALB&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3. Lattice - unknown tech, will the target groups work as expected?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4. Type of MP account - member vs unrestricted account&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;5. Deployments? MP pipelines for platform infra, Concourse for user infra?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;6. Authentication to platform and cluster&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry height="705" width="630" x="1800" y="1062" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
    </diagram>
</mxfile>